      "representative_excerpt": "I am in support of this proposal. Shutting down electrical facilities may produce the desired affect, but overall, the decision will have backlash. Haze pollution is an issue that has cropped up more than once, but we cannot get rid of one problem by creating another; that\u2019s counterintuitive, especially for a state a small as Hawaii.",
