      "representative_length": 290,
      "representative_excerpt": "I am in favor of this proposal because of the need to have clean air balanced with the needs to keep Hawaii\u2019s power grid functional. People will likely be against any delays in plant closures, but I think this step is needed to protect our energy security while chasing environmental goals.",
